data.description:
Nestled in the highly sought-after community of Smoky Ridge, this stunning multi level home with a finished basement is a true gem. The grand entryway welcomes you with soaring ceilings, leading to the formal dining room and living area, creating a sense of elegance and space.

The well-appointed eat-in kitchen features beautiful updates including trendy white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and striking quartz countertops. Large windows in the kitchen and dinette area offer picturesque views of the private backyard, complete with mature landscaping, a covered patio, custom pavers, and a convenient shed for outdoor storage.

Step down from the dinette area into the cozy living room, perfect for relaxing by the fireplace or socializing with guests. The lower level also includes a versatile bedroom that can double as a private office, along with a powder room, laundry closet, and access to the oversized 2-car garage.

Upstairs, the primary suite boasts a spacious walk-in closet and an updated ensuite bathroom with a relaxing soaking tub and shower. Two additional large bedrooms share a full bathroom on this level.

The finished basement adds even more living space, featuring another bedroom, a full bathroom, and ample room for recreation or a home gym. With a brand new furnace and water heater, major mechanical worries are minimized for the buyer.

Smoky Ridge offers walking paths, centrally located to DIA, Denver Tech Centerl, Quincy Reservoir, shopping, dining,and access to exemplary Cherry Creek schools, making it more than just a neighborhood—it's a lifestyle destination.
